                        <h2 class="text-md">About Me</h2>
                        <div class="divider my-4"></div>
                        <p>I am a board-certified orthopedic surgeon with over 15 years of experience in diagnosing and
                            treating musculoskeletal conditions. My approach to patient care centers on utilizing the
                            latest minimally invasive surgical techniques to reduce recovery time and improve overall
                            mobility. I believe in working closely with my patients to develop personalized treatment
                            plans that restore function and alleviate pain.</p>
                        <p>Throughout my career, I have successfully performed thousands of joint replacement and trauma
                            surgeries. I am deeply committed to continuing education and frequently participate in
                            medical research to stay at the forefront of orthopedic advancements, ensuring my patients
                            receive the highest standard of care possible.</p>

                        <a href="appoinment" class="btn btn-main-2 btn-round-full mt-3">Make an Appointment<i
                                class="icofont-simple-right ml-2  "></i></a>
